      "description": "This vehicle is in impeccable, showroom condition, having been preserved with the utmost care. The exterior finish is flawless, and the interior retains its original factory-fresh scent and appearance. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the dealership, with no signs of wear or aging. It represents a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a truly pristine example.",
